<p><span class="flagicon"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9c/Flag_of_Brunei.svg/22px-Flag_of_Brunei.svg.png" width="22" height="11" class="thumbborder" />&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Brunei" title="Brunei">Brunei</a><br />
<span class="flagicon"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/48/Flag_of_Singapore.svg/22px-Flag_of_Singapore.svg.png" width="22" height="15" class="thumbborder" />&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Singapore" title="Singapore">Singapore</a><br />
<span class="flagicon"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9f/Flag_of_Indonesia.svg/22px-Flag_of_Indonesia.svg.png" width="22" height="15" class="thumbborder" />&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Indonesia" title="Indonesia">Indonesia</a> <small>(as <a href="/wiki/Indonesian_language" title="Indonesian language">Indonesian</a><sup id="cite_ref-Indonesian_language_0-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Indonesian_language-0"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup>)</small><br />
<span class="flagicon"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/26/Flag_of_East_Timor.svg/22px-Flag_of_East_Timor.svg.png" width="22" height="11" class="thumbborder" />&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/East_Timor" title="East Timor">East Timor</a> <small>(as <a href="/wiki/Indonesian_language" title="Indonesian language">Indonesian</a><sup id="cite_ref-Indonesian_language_0-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Indonesian_language-0"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup>)</small><br />
<span class="flagicon"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/99/Flag_of_the_Philippines.svg/22px-Flag_of_the_Philippines.svg.png" width="22" height="11" class="thumbborder" />&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Philippines" title="Philippines">Philippines</a> <small>(mostly in <a href="/wiki/Tawi_Tawi" title="Tawi Tawi" class="mw-redirect">Tawi Tawi</a> and <a href="/wiki/Sulu" title="Sulu">Sulu</a>)<sup class="Template-Fact" title="This claim needs references to reliable sources from May 2011" style="white-space:nowrap;">[<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed" title="Wikipedia:Citation needed">citation needed</a></i>]</sup></small><br />
<span class="flagicon"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a9/Flag_of_Thailand.svg/22px-Flag_of_Thailand.svg.png" width="22" height="15" class="thumbborder" />&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Thailand" title="Thailand">Thailand</a><br />
<span class="flagicon"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8c/Flag_of_Myanmar.svg/22px-Flag_of_Myanmar.svg.png" width="22" height="15" class="thumbborder" />&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Myanmar" title="Myanmar" class="mw-redirect">Myanmar</a><br />
<span class="flagicon"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/11/Flag_of_Sri_Lanka.svg/22px-Flag_of_Sri_Lanka.svg.png" width="22" height="11" class="thumbborder" />&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Sri_Lanka" title="Sri Lanka">Sri Lanka</a><br />
<span class="flagicon"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/74/Flag_of_the_Cocos_%28Keeling%29_Islands.svg/22px-Flag_of_the_Cocos_%28Keeling%29_Islands.svg.png" width="22" height="11" class="thumbborder" />&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Cocos_(Keeling)_Islands" title="Cocos (Keeling) Islands">Cocos (Keeling) Islands</a><sup id="cite_ref-Malay_in_Australian_islands_1-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Malay_in_Australian_islands-1"><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup><br />
<span class="flagicon"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/67/Flag_of_Christmas_Island.svg/22px-Flag_of_Christmas_Island.svg.png" width="22" height="11" class="thumbborder" />&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Christmas_Island" title="Christmas Island">Christmas Island</a><sup id="cite_ref-Malay_in_Australian_islands_1-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Malay_in_Australian_islands-1"><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
